| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5044 — Recovery Inhibition (medusalocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a6cedbaa-26c5-50c8-8372-89a5857c6a99"
